{"tid":1116134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【首都專線】賞花變摧花　當局擬定遊園黑名單","createTime":"2019-04-19T17:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T01:54:35.000Z","uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0f3fd7b7252762e7b2af5423a0265712cdb6bc30","tid":1116134,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T17:00:53.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】北京玉淵潭公園每年春天都會舉辦櫻花節，吸引遊客來賞花及拍照，為令照片拍得好，大家都有一套「攝影技巧」。<br />\n<br />\n一片櫻花海，用手機拍攝最方便，認真點帶備相機，效果自然不一樣。只得櫻花有點單調，站在櫻花樹下來一張人比花嬌如何？想拉近同櫻花的距離，竟然選擇「出手」。忍不到出手的不止她一人，捕捉不到綿綿頭上飛花，不是等，而是搖，有人更用上洪荒之力。<br />\n<br />\n針對這些摧花行為，當局近日在樹上掛出告示牌，並加派人員提醒遊客文明賞花，距離產生美，在拍照時請你和櫻花樹保持距離，有人盯着，遊人都守規矩。<br />\n<br />\n北京市屬公園正研究制訂遊園黑名單制度，計劃在公園入口設立人臉識別裝置，篩查因為不文明或破壞行為被列入黑名單的人，拒絕他們入園。<br />\n<br />\n北京旅遊學會副秘書長劉思敏表示，設立遊園黑名單的初衷是好，但具體執行有難度。他認為不文明旅遊不是一時三刻可以解決，長遠而言，必須在家庭、學校和社會三個層面教育公眾，才可提高旅客質素。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=345055\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D345055&d=v6UOKjiqNHu3M1gE0B2GLHljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=3ccf1b92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D345055&h=b58a59f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=345055</a>"},{"pid":"08672c5571801a71b8a0e9fb492b09de6ff53d18","tid":1116134,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T17:35:42.000Z","msg":"必須在家庭、學校和社會三個層面教育公眾，才可提高旅客質素<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e70720ba2f58034cc1e2f12672bd94f1097dee","tid":1116134,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T17:58:32.000Z","msg":"生番賞櫻"},{"pid":"fde8ad56166fece447cd5d9c66c9f8394a2028f6","tid":1116134,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T01:54:35.000Z","msg":"賞櫻花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜共剷支那人有賞櫻花既習俗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呀雜種做乜唔拉曬呢班精日份子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}